OL,3,CShop prices fall in August for first
OL,4,Ctime in nearly three years, figures
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FPrices in shops are falling for the
OL,8,Ffirst time in nearly three years, new
OL,9,Ffigures show.
OL,11,FRetailers slashing prices to get rid
OL,12,Fof summer stock helped overall shop
OL,13,Fprices fall into deflation in August
OL,14,Ffor the first time since October 2021,
OL,15,Faccording to an influential retail
OL,16,Fgroup.
OL,18,FDeflation is when the general level of
OL,19,Fprices for goods and services
OL,20,Fdecreases, and happens when the
OL,21,Finflation rate falls below 0%.
