OL,3,CShop prices fall in August for first
OL,4,Ctime in nearly three years, figures
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FShop prices in August were 0.3% lower
OL,8,Fthan a year earlier, the British
OL,9,FRetail Consortium (BRC)-NielsenIQ Shop
OL,10,FPrice Index found.
OL,12,FThe figure is down from inflation of
OL,13,F0.2% in July and below the three-month
OL,14,Faverage rate of 0%.
OL,16,FThe survey period covered the first
OL,17,Fweek of August.
