OL,3,CShop prices fall in August for first
OL,4,Ctime in nearly three years, figures
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FThe overall decline was driven by
OL,8,Fdeflation of 1.5% of "non-food"
OL,9,Fproducts, which refers to products
OL,10,Flike clothing, furniture and
OL,11,Felectronics.
OL,13,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,14,Fthe BRC, said it reflects "retailers
OL,15,Fdiscounting heavily to shift their
OL,16,Fsummer stock, particularly for fashion
OL,17,Fand household goods".
