OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,F"This discounting followed a difficult
OL,8,Fsummer of trading caused by poor
OL,9,Fweather and the continued cost-of-
OL,10,Fliving crunch impacting many
OL,11,Ffamilies," she said.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, food prices increased by 2%
OL,14,Fin August, compared with the previous
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FNevertheless, the rate that prices are
OL,18,Frising continues to slow, and this
OL,19,Fmonth was the lowest since November
OL,20,F2021.
