OL,3,CShop prices fall in August for first
OL,4,Ctime in nearly three years, figures
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,F"Retailers will continue to work hard
OL,8,Fto keep prices down, and households
OL,9,Fwill be happy to see that prices of
OL,10,Fsome goods have fallen into
OL,11,Fdeflation," Ms Dickinson said.
OL,13,F"The outlook for commodity prices
OL,14,Fremains uncertain due to the impact of
OL,15,Fclimate change on harvests
OL,16,Fdomestically and globally, as well as
OL,17,Frising geopolitical tensions.
OL,19,F"As a result, we could see renewed
OL,20,Finflationary pressures over the next
OL,21,Fyear."
